While checking the configuration of the communication system, Daemos 
stumbled on a msg sent by the IGL. It had been received some times before he 
landed on Earth. After reviewing it, he decided to register.

Daemos:
This message is destined to the IGL. I am Daemos of the Tripredacus. I will 
compete in the Regular Division. Since I am a newcomer, register me as a 
member of the tripredacus faction.
